      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i just cut my forearm really bad while cooking. it's a pretty deep gash and it keeps oozing blood even when i press on it. i dont really want to go to the clinic if i dont have to... would putting some honey on it and wrapping it up work? i heard honey is good for healing wounds",
